  "texts": [
    "Following the same protocol as above, we evaluate ATLA's performance with four different suffix lengths, which are 5, 7, 9, and 12.",
    "We run each setup for first 50 harmful questions.",
    "The results are presented in Fig. 15.",
    "ATLA is robust with respect to different suffix length choices.",
    "Moreover, ATLA can learn an adversarial suffix easier when the suffix length is longer."
  ]
}